      "rationale": "Bilinear isotropic hardening plasticity model used for titanium alloy (Ti-6Al-4V). Constitutive parameters calibrated against tensile coupon data from the same material lot. Geometric nonlinearity (large deformation) enabled to capture post-yield response. Contact between screw and rod modeled with penalty-based frictional contact (mu=0.2)."
