      "rationale": "Testing performed per ASTM F1717 protocol at 23°C, 5 mm/min crosshead speed, using standardized polyethylene blocks. However, only a single loading condition (static compression-bending) was evaluated; fatigue and dynamic loading conditions were not included in this validation activity. This limitation reduces the achieved level to 2, below the required level of 3. Risk accepted given the COU is restricted to static compression-bending prediction only."
