      "rationale": "FEA model geometry derived from CAD nominal with CMM-measured deviations applied as perturbations. Material properties in FEA matched to certified test report values used to fabricate the tested specimens. Boundary conditions replicate ASTM F1717 fixture geometry with fixture compliance measured and incorporated. Residual input equivalency uncertainty estimated at 1.8% of QoI."
