      "rationale": "E/uval computed per ASME V&V 40 Section 9 for all three QoIs: stiffness (E/uval=0.87), yield force (E/uval=1.31), force at 40 mm (E/uval=1.14). All values below the 1.96 threshold. Percent differences (4.2%, 6.1%, 5.8%) all within the 10% acceptance bound. Model adequacy confirmed for the stated COU."
