    "rationale": "Thirteen V&V 40 credibility factors assessed. Twelve of thirteen factors meet or exceed the required level for Medium model risk. One factor (Test conditions) achieved level 2 against a required level of 3 due to single loading condition; this gap is accepted because the COU is explicitly scoped to static compression-bending only and the regulatory decision consequence is Medium. Quantitative output comparison (E/uval < 1.96 for all QoIs; percent differences < 10%) confirms model adequacy. Overall credibility is sufficient to support the Accepted decision for the stated COU.",
